add_item(({"ground","landscape","terrain", "forest bed", "forest floor"}),
         "The forest bed is a lush riot of flowers and plants.  "
         "Small rocks with velvety moss crawling over them dot the "
         "landscape.\n");
add_item("road","A small road winds its way from the village, Unicorn Cove, "
         "to the base of Unicorn Mountain.  Along its journey it passes "
         "through the beautiful Southern forest.\n");
add_item(({"trail","path"}),"Small, leaf strewn trails criss-cross the "
         "Southern forest.\n");
add_item("forest","A place of magic and wonder, the Southern Forest is an "
         "enchanting combination of magic and nature.  Home to some of "
         "the realms' most beautiful and exotic plants, the forest is "
         "truly one of the most spectacular places you will ever visit.\n");
add_item("greenery","Bright, vibrant plants fill the Southern Forest with "
         "colour and magic.\n");
add_item(({"bush","shrubbery","shrub"}),"Small, leafy bushes surround the "
         "forest trails in a collage of greens and grays.\n");
add_item("tree","Tall and magnificent, the trees forming the Southern "
         "Forest radiate life and love.  Their branches stretch high "
         "into the sky, as if to pull Unicorn Mountain closer to the "
         "heavens.\n");
add_item("branch","Long branches, covered in leaves, stretch out from "
         "their trees, as if ready to embrace the realms.\n");
add_item(({"leaves","leaf"}),"Fanning out over the trail, beautiful and "
         "rich in colour, these leaves are testament to the powerful life "
         "force protecting Unicorn Mountain.\n");
add_item(({"plant","flower"}),"The forest bed is a vibrant backdrop of "
         "small, delicate plants and beautiful, exotic flowers.\n");
add_item("village","In the distance, you can see the outline of beautiful "
         "and prosperous village.  Unicorn Cove is a bee-hive of activity "
         "from dawn to dusk.\n");
add_item(({"mountain","peaks"}),"Unicorn Mountain is perhaps the most "
         "spectacular sight in all the realms.  Tall peaks in purples "
         "and blues, shot through with threads of silver rise high into "
         "the clouds.  An aura of magic and serenity surround the mountain "
         "like a protective shield.\n");
add_item("birds","Bright, colourfully plumed birds dart in and out of the "
         "trees to the accompaniment of a symphony of birdsong.\n");
add_item(({"animals","deer","wildlife"}),"You see a menagerie of forest "
         "animals scurrying about the area.  Deer dart across the path "
         "in front of you, while squirrels and rabbits play amongst the "
         "plants.\n");
add_item("shadows","Leaves and branches cast soft shadows across the "
         "trail.\n");
add_item("canopy","The tops of the trees form a brightly coloured "
         "playground for birds and squirrels.  The canopy of the Southern "
         "Forest is a riot of sound and activity.\n");
add_item("sky","The sky is a deep, rich blue.  The air sparkles and shines.  "
         "Small, puffy clouds are carried gently across the horizon on the "
         "wind.\n");
add_item("moss","The moss covering the rocks along the forest bed is like "
         "a rich green velvet curtain of life.\n");
add_feel("magic","The Southern Forest hums with a magic so strong that it "
         "almost crackles through the air.  Fueled by the enchantment "
         "surrounding the unicorn, the forest thrives beyond that which "
         "even nature, in all its perfection, can produce.\n");
add_feel("innocence","The magic of the unicorn is such that nothing evil "
         "or malicious can touch that which it protects.  This area retains "
         "that touch of innocence that comes from never knowing of evil.\n");
add_feel("mystery","The air of mystery surrounding that fabled creature of "
         "lore, the unicorn, can be felt throughout the forest.\n");
add_feel("cheer","The Southern forest instills within you a sense of joy "
         "and cheer.  Life at its best is contained within these trees.\n");
add_feel("power","Power thrums through the air, sweeping across you with "
         "shivery little tingles.\n");
add_feel("breeze","A gentle breeze whispers quietly through the forest.\n");
add_feel(({"tree","bark","branch"}),"the bark of the trees is a collage of "
         "roughly interlocking pieces.\n");
add_feel("plants","The leaves fall through your fingers like the delicate, "
         "smooth brush of silk against your skin.\n");
add_feel("moss","The moss feels thick and springy.\n");
add_smell(({"air","breeze","forest"}),"The forest is a spicey blend of "
          "scents.  You smell, all at once, the rich, pungent odor of the "
          "earth mixed with the musky exotic scent of rare flowers, as well "
          "as, the sweet, fresh scents of pine and cedar.\n");
add_smell("flower","A musky, heady scent is released by the exotic flowers "
          "of the Southern Forest.\n");
add_sound(({"birdsong","birds","melody"}),"You hear the sweet trills of a "
          "multitude of birds in song, accompanied by the swift fluttering "
          "of wings, as the birds take flight.\n");
add_sound("village","Even from a distance, the hustle and bustle of "
          "thriving Unicorn Cove can be heard.\n");

         
